name: Blume Number 4
description:
4k Resolution 2160x3840px .gif, digital collage/painting. by Bryant W.

This digital collage design is a combination of years of work from photos to old illustrations mashed into a fleeting beauty forever hiding behind a walled pattern.


The Eyes are the Window to the Soul and Yet Our Ego gets in the way of Seeing what is right in Front of us! - Bryant W.
